  "chatSystemAutoPlayful001V1": "Suspicion is already in the air… and nobody has confessed a thing.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful002V1": "Now that the draw is done, every innocent question sounds strategic.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful003V1": "Tarci tip: investigate with subtlety, not like an interrogation.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful004V1": "Some already have a gift. Others have faith.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful005V1": "If someone asks about sizes, colors and hobbies all at once, take note.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful006V1": "A good gift surprises. A great gift becomes a story.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful007V1": "Suspicious smiles count as clues.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful008V1": "Misdirection is allowed. Overdoing it is not recommended.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful009V1": "Some people's silence is starting to look like a plan.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful010V1": "If you are going to improvise, at least improvise with care.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful011V1": "Tarci detects energy for epic gifts… and elegant panic.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful012V1": "Anyone saying “I already have it” without proof raises suspicion.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful013V1": "Friendly reminder: the mystery is part of the fun.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful014V1": "Every group has a detective. Do you already know who it is?",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful015V1": "A thoughtful detail is worth more than a gift without soul.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful016V1": "This chat is officially in suspicion mode.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful017V1": "If you just searched for gift ideas in secret, nobody is judging.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful018V1": "Some real-life glances suddenly mean far too much.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful019V1": "The mission is not to spend more. It is to get it right.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful020V1": "Hiding it well is also part of the game.",
  "chatSystemAutoPlayful021V1": "Tarci bets someone here already has a brilliant plan.",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate001V1": "Quick debate: a useful gift or a gift that makes people laugh?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate002V1": "Better a total surprise or a well-used hint?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate003V1": "What wins: creativity or precision?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate004V1": "Open debate: does spectacular wrapping matter?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate005V1": "Discreet research or wish list to the rescue?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate006V1": "Without naming names: who in this group improvises at the last minute?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate007V1": "A small gift with a story or a big gift without one?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate008V1": "Is misdirection in the chat fair play or already dirty tactics?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate009V1": "What feels better: getting it right or surprising someone?",
  "chatSystemAutoDebate010V1": "If you had to choose: practical, fun or sentimental?",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist001V1": "Some wish lists are still empty. A timely hint can save a gift.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist002V1": "Your wish list does not remove the magic; it avoids guessing blindly.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist003V1": "If you want them to get it right, leave a few ideas.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist004V1": "Someone is preparing a gift with very few clues. Ahem.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist005V1": "Filling in your list helps without revealing too much.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist006V1": "A link, a preference, a clue: it all helps.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist007V1": "Even the best surprises appreciate a little guidance.",
  "chatSystemAutoWishlist008V1": "If your list is empty, your Secret Santa is playing on hard mode.",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet001V1": "It is very quiet here… shopping or hiding evidence?",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet002V1": "This group is far too quiet. Someone break the ice.",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet003V1": "Tarci is taking attendance: is the playful chaos still alive?",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet004V1": "Reactivation question: who looks most suspicious today?",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet005V1": "If nobody writes, Tarci will start making up theories.",
  "chatSystemAutoQuiet006V1": "Sleeping chat, wide-awake mystery. Say something.",
  "chatSystemAutoCountdown014V1": "14 days left. There is still time, but excuses are running out.",
  "chatSystemAutoCountdown007V1": "7 days left. Anyone without an idea has officially entered serious search mode.",
  "chatSystemAutoCountdown003V1": "3 days left. This is no longer planning; it is a rescue operation.",
  "chatSystemAutoCountdown001V1": "1 day left. Wrap it, breathe, and act natural.",
  "chatSystemAutoCountdown000V1": "Today is the exchange. May there be surprises, laughs, and zero early confessions.",
